possibly called you

17:17.384 --> 17:18.950
was to apologize.

17:19.038 --> 17:21.083
I guess.

17:21.170 --> 17:22.911
And she knew
you were coming.

17:22.998 --> 17:24.869
That had to give her some peace.

17:24.956 --> 17:28.308
Yeah.

17:28.395 --> 17:31.702
Hey, you guys want to help me
with the funeral arrangements?

17:31.789 --> 17:32.486
I'd be honored.

17:32.573 --> 17:34.488
Of course.

17:40.059 --> 17:44.585
You know, this reminds me
of a story.

17:44.672 --> 17:45.760
No!

17:45.847 --> 17:46.891
No, wait, just hear me out.

17:46.978 --> 17:50.373
Once upon a time,

17:50.460 --> 17:53.811
