to make his way in the world.

17:57.511 --> 17:58.990
In his travels,
he met a man

17:59.078 --> 18:00.862
who became like
a father to him,

18:00.949 --> 18:03.778
who helped him become the king

18:03.865 --> 18:04.953
he was always destined to be.

18:05.040 --> 18:08.826
And his reign was long and just,

18:08.913 --> 18:13.048
